        <h1>Data transfer: Modbus slave</h1>
        <table style="width: 100%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 13.699%;" />
            <col style="width: 86.301%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td style="width: 13.699%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;" valign="bottom" width="13.699%">
                    <p class="PercorsoIntroduzioneTabella">Path:<img src="../Resources/Images/ico_white23x22.jpg" style="border: none;width: 23px;height: 22px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="23" height="22" border="0" /></p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 86.301%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;" valign="bottom" width="86.301%">
                    <p class="PercorsoIntroduzioneTabella"><span style="font-weight: normal;"><img src="../Resources/Images/menusx/new/calendar3.png" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 31px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="31" border="0" />, <a href="Trasferimento_dati__introduzione.htm">Data transfer</a></span><span style="font-weight: normal;">, page  </span>Modbus Slave</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td style="width: 13.699%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-left-style: none;border-right-style: none;border-bottom-style: none;" width="13.699%">
                    <p class="PercorsoIntroduzioneTabella">Access:</p>
                </td>
                <td style="width: 86.301%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;border-bottom-style: none;border-right-style: None;" width="86.301%">
                    <p class="PercorsoIntroduzioneTabella">Installers</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p>&#160;</p>
        <table style="border-left-style: Solid;border-top-style: Solid;border-right-style: Solid;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-left-width: 2px;border-right-width: 2px;border-top-width: 2px;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-left-color: #5f5f5f;border-right-color: #5f5f5f;border-top-color: #5f5f5f;border-bottom-color: #5f5f5f;width: 100%;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
            <col style="width: 15.979%;" />
            <col style="width: 84.021%;" />
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-top-width: 3px;border-top-style: Solid;border-top-color: #ffffff;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Purpose</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-top-width: 3px;border-top-color: #ffffff;border-top-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p>Lets variable groups recognized by BMS to be set as a Modbus device. </p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">Description</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p>PVPRO variables (Digital, Alarm, Integer and Analog type) are automatically mapped on Modbus data types:</p>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p style="font-style: italic;">coil <span style="font-style: normal;">(Digital and Alarms)</span></p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p style="font-style: italic;">register <span style="font-style: normal;">(Integer and Analog).</span></p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p style="font-style: normal;">Coil and Register have two different addresses. Thus it is normal to have the same address for two types of Modbus variables</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-width: 3px;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">What to do first</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-width: 3px;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p>-</p>
                </td>
            </tr>
            <tr valign="top">
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 15.979%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #c9c9c9;border-left-color: #ffffff;border-left-style: Solid;border-left-width: 3px;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#C9C9C9" width="15.979%">
                    <p style="font-weight: bold;">What to do next</p>
                </td>
                <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 84.021%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #eaeaea;border-right-color: #ffffff;border-right-style: Solid;border-right-width: 3px;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 3px;" bgcolor="#EAEAEA" width="84.021%">
                    <p>Start ModbusSlave service in <span style="font-weight: bold;">Configuration, System page, System</span>. Subsequent settings changes are applied when the service is rebooted from this page.</p>
                    <table style="width: 100%;border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#C0C0C0" width="100%">
                        <col style="width: 7.585%;" />
                        <col style="width: 92.415%;" />
                        <tr valign="top">
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 7.585%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="7.585%">
                                <p class="Note">
                                    <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                                </p>
                            </td>
                            <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 92.415%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="92.415%">
                                <p>The reboot key is only enabled if ModbusSlave service is running. See <span style="font-weight: bold;">Configuration, System page, System</span>.</p>
                            </td>
                        </tr>
                    </table>
                </td>
            </tr>
        </table>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /> Action</p>
        <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_">Set connection parameters
                                                                </a></span>
            <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Connection configuration</span> select the connection mode with BMS. TCP/IP protocol is set by default on port 502. </p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_"><span style="background-color: Transparent;">Add a Modbus device</span></a></span>
                    <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                        <div>
                            <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                                <li class="p" value="1">
                                    <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Device name</span> indicate the name to assign to the variable group to be displayed.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="p" value="2">
                                    <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Device address</span> select an address from those available.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="p" value="3">
                                    <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Device</span> select device PVPRO, filtering the device list using the <span style="font-weight: bold;">Device models</span> menu if necessary.</p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="p" value="4">
                                    <p>To select variables:</p>
                                </li>
                                <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                                    <li class="p" value="1">
                                        <p>Select the variables and click <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/addsmall_on.png" style="border: none;width: 19px;height: 19px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="19" height="19" border="0" />: an incremental address, starting from zero, is automatically assigned to the variable, and appears on section <span style="font-weight: bold;">Current configuration</span></p>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                            </ul>
                            <p style="margin-left: 88px;font-weight: normal;">or</p>
                            <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                                <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                                    <li class="p" value="1">
                                        <p>in <span style="font-weight: bold;">Next Coil/Next register</span> indicate any address</p>
                                    </li>
                                    <li class="p" value="2">
                                        <p>Select a variable and click <img src="../Resources/Images/dbllistbox/addsmall_on.png" style="border: none;width: 19px;height: 19px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="19" height="19" border="0" />: the indicated address is assigned to the variable and appears in section <span style="font-weight: bold;">Current configuration</span></p>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <li class="p" value="2">
                                    <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/add_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 24px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="24" border="0" /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Add</span>: the set variable group is added to the <span style="font-weight: bold;">Modbus device </span>section. </p>
                                </li>
                                <li class="p" value="3">
                                    <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /></p>
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                            <table style="width: 100%;border-left-color: #000000;border-left-width: 1px;border-right-color: #000000;border-right-width: 1px;background-color: #c0c0c0;border-spacing: 0px;border-spacing: 0px;" cellspacing="0" bgcolor="#C0C0C0" width="100%">
                                <col style="width: 7.585%;" />
                                <col style="width: 92.415%;" />
                                <tr valign="top">
                                    <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 7.585%;padding-right: 10px;padding-left: 10px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-style: Solid;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-width: 2px;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" valign="middle" width="7.585%">
                                        <p class="Note">
                                            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAinfo.gif" style="border: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />
                                        </p>
                                    </td>
                                    <td colspan="1" rowspan="1" style="width: 92.415%;padding-right: 1px;padding-left: 1px;background-color: #cccccc;border-bottom-width: 2px;border-bottom-color: #ffffff;border-bottom-style: Solid;" bgcolor="#CCCCCC" width="92.415%">
                                        <p>the total counter appears in <span style="font-weight: bold;">Configured variables</span> and cannot exceed the value indicated in <span style="font-weight: bold;">Supported variables.</span></p>
                                    </td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            <p>&#160;</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_"><span style="background-color: Transparent;">Enable set R/W variable to writing</span></a></span>
            <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>Select <span style="font-weight: bold;">Enable write function</span></p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Save</span>: after rebooting the service, BMS can only write on enabled variables (column <span style="font-weight: bold;">Read only</span> not selected).</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_"><span style="background-color: Transparent;">Delete a Modbus device&#160;</span></a></span>
            <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Modbus devices</span> select the Modbus device to be deleted.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/remove2_on.png" style="border: none;width: 28px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="28" height="28" border="0" /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Delete</span></p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /></p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_">Delete one or more variables from a Modbus device
                                                                </a></span>
            <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>In <span style="font-weight: bold;">Modbus devices</span> select the Modbus device to be edited.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="2">
                            <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/Edit_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 24px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="24" border="0" /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Modify</span>: the device variables appear in section <span style="font-weight: bold;">Current configuration</span></p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="3">
                            <p style="font-weight: normal;">Select a variable and click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/remove_on_black.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 24px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="24" border="0" /> . Repeat for each variable to be deleted.</p>
                        </li>
                        <li class="p" value="4">
                            <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/save_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 28px;float: none;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="28" border="0" /></p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="MCDropDown MCDropDown_Open dropDown"><span class="MCDropDownHead dropDownHead"><a href="javascript:void(0);" class="MCDropDownHotSpot dropDownHotspot MCDropDownHotSpot_">Reboot the service
                                                                </a></span>
            <div class="MCDropDownBody dropDownBody">
                <div>
                    <ul style="list-style: disc;" type="disc">
                        <li class="p" value="1">
                            <p>Click <img src="../Resources/Images/actions/reset_button.png" style="border: none;width: 24px;height: 24px;float: none;border-style: none;" width="24" height="24" border="0" /> <span style="font-weight: bold;">Restart: </span><span style="font-weight: bold;"> <![CDATA[ ]]></span>ModbusSlave service is restarted and all changes are applied.</p>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <p class="TitoloInterno">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAaction.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" /> Other actions</p>
        <p>Common used buttons</p>
        <p class="ActionDetail">
            <img src="../Resources/Images/AAvedianche.gif" style="border: none;float: none;width: 32px;height: 32px;border-style: none;border-style: none;" width="32" height="32" border="0" />See also</p>
        <p>-</p>
